<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="16" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="15.[264,1325,879,1785]" box="[264,789,879,905]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
Coloration and structure as in 
<taxonomicName box="[618,789,879,904]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Varta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubrostriata">
<emphasis box="[618,789,879,904]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">V. rubrostriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[264,1325,879,1785]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
<emphasis box="[312,488,919,944]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Male genitalia</emphasis>
: Pygophore with dorsal membranous lobe extending caudally along with ventral sclerotized process, which is caudally curved ventrally; a few (
<number box="[1169,1215,959,985]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="2.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.0">2–3</number>
) setae at base dorsad of membranous lobe. Segment X elongate with slightly longer toothlike processes holding the apex of aedeagal shaft in place. Style with well­developed preapical lobe, apophysis of style laterally curved, rugulose with a tooth before apex. Connective as in 
<taxonomicName box="[300,476,1119,1144]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Varta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubrostriata">
<emphasis box="[300,476,1119,1144]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">V. rubrostriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Aedeagus with well­developed dorsal apodeme, shaft strongly constricted and with a triangular process at base, uneven in width, slightly narrowed at mid length, apex strongly caudally curved, with a dorsal ridge, gonopore on caudal region, process beneath gonopore straight, directed caudo­ventrally.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[264,1325,879,1785]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
<emphasis box="[312,482,1279,1304]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Measurements</emphasis>
: Male 
<quantity box="[568,660,1279,1305]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.9" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="5.9">5.9 mm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity box="[737,829,1279,1305]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="1.3">1.3 mm</quantity>
wide across hind margin of head and 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" unit="mm" value="1.4">1.4 mm</quantity>
wide across hind margin of pronotum.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
